  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Each character has five unique attacks to them. Each time you attack with
    a certain character in your turn, they will use the first attack which is often
    their weakest. Then the next button press is a slightly stronger attack, and
    so on until the fifth unique attack.


    Every character''s fifth attack is
    an "ultimate" attack that does a greater amount of damage then their previous
    ones. The catch is that once a character reaches their ultimate, the player''s
    turn ends and the enemy turn begins. So a good strategy is to think ahead about
    which character''s ultimate you want to use, and space out your attacks across
    all rounds of your turn to prolong reaching the ultimate and maximizing the damage
    dealt. An experienced player can defeat a high health enemy in one turn if they
    execute their attacks correctly.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
