  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'This game is a turn based RPG where you control a party of four characters
    with the goal of defeating all of the waves of enemies in battle.


    Each
    of the four characters is tied to a key on the keyboard (I, O, K, L) and pressing
    one of the buttons makes the corresponing character attack the selected enemy.
    At the start if your turn, you have a total of five button presses (attacks)
    to use between the four characters, and these can be distributed however you
    wish. However, you must think and act quickly, because after your first attack
    a combo window starts and if you don''t attack soon enough the combo will drop
    and the enemy turn will start. If you reach a certain damage treshold (tracked
    in the bottom left corner), you get a chance at a QTE event to earn another round
    of five more attacks and continue your turn. The damage trheshold increases by
    100 each round, but each character''s attacks do more damage as the rounds continue.
    Press space to execute the QTE.


'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
